title: Bodybuilding - Frank Zane - Audio interview
description:
This is a great interview with Frank Zane from the Super Strength Show.

The wonderful thing about Zane is that he is straight forward and, holds nothing back.  Since he doesn't rely on big companies for backing, you get some honest truth from a legendary bodybuilder and, intelligent man.

Runtime 65 minutes.
Bitrate is 128 kbps.
